Staraptor (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0397: Staravia
Pokémon
#0399: Bidoof →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Staraptor (TCG Pocket).

Staraptor has been featured on 11 different cards since it debuted in the Diamond & Pearl expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Staraptor cards are normally Colorless-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Staraptor

Staraptor
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
